V3 of zm_bunker_f57

Changes included in this version:

- Added new hallways, stairways, rooms and secrets.
- Removed areaportals from doubledoors.
- Improved optimision.
- "Better" brushwork.
- Fixed a few places where players might get stuck.
- Modified the double-doors to not missbehave anymore.
- Minor details addings and improving the hallway looks.
- Changed alarm sound.

This map is fully optimized! FPS test results:

Tested with a laptop: 200-250 fps.
Tested with a desktop: 500-600 fps.

Max. players: 60
Recommended players: 50
Map size: Medium
Mapfile size: 4,3 MB

There are no custom content on this map! Everything should be working perfectly! Please, report any missing textures/models if there are any.
